# Implement product supplier context menu (2025-12-06 05:45Z)

_**User (2025-12-06 05:32Z)**_

in /admin/products, add another menu option to the right-click on a specific product: Assign Supplier or Change Supplier (if one is selected).  It opens the same kind of dialog that Bulk assign Supplier has except we might be able to just add a fly-out to the Assign/Change supplier menu which is a submenu with the list of suppliers to choose from. Exclude the currently selected supplier (if non null/empty)
